| T2 | Extract shared reactive-loop fragment for Taskmaster/Subtaskmaster/Reviewer | `agents/_fragments/reactive-loop.md`, update 3 templates, re-run expand-templates | 1 worker, `opus` |
| T3 | Cap `on-pre-compact.sh` output to ≤ 50 lines + gate verbose behind env var | `.claude/hooks/on-pre-compact.sh` | 1 worker, `sonnet` |
| T4 | Consolidate 7 `feedback_proof_*.md` memory files into one | user memory dir | 1 worker, `sonnet` quick |
| T5 | Move `doey-masterplan` and `doey-add-team` bash bodies to `<name>.sh`, slim SKILL.md | `.claude/skills/doey-masterplan/`, `doey-add-team/` | 1 worker, `sonnet` |
| T6 | Clip `_auto_output` in `stop-results.sh` so failed go build noise can't balloon result JSON | `.claude/hooks/stop-results.sh:205-246` | 1 worker, `sonnet` quick |
| T7 | Fresh-install integrity: fail loudly when `doey-roles.sh` not found; add `doey doctor` check for hook presence | `.claude/hooks/on-pre-tool-use.sh:46-71`, `shell/doey-doctor.sh` | 1 worker, `sonnet` |
| T8 | web-install: persist repo to `~/.local/share/doey/source/` before running `install.sh` | `web-install.sh` | 1 worker, `sonnet` |
